<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n18171b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n18" href="#n18171b">N18 (VI.B.8)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n18all.htm#n18171b"> 171(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> massage </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: The massage was part of a therapy to cure deafness, during which the interior of the ear is &lsquo;massaged&rsquo; with artificially created sounds or vowels. Thus the tympane is agitated and revived in a permanent way. The apparatus which is used is called &ldquo;la sir&egrave;ne&ldquo; or &rdquo;tympano-masseur&rdquo;. </mm> </dd></dl>
